BFN 

  [Text] Moscow, May 24 (XINHUA) -- Russian ambassador to 
Yemen sent a letter from Russian leaders to president of the 
Yemeni Presidential Committee on Monday [23 May], expressing 
support for the unity and stability of Yemen, the ITAR-TASS NEWS 
AGENCY said. 
  Russian leaders said in the letter that Russia would be 
closely concerned for the development of the situation in Yemen. 
  They also said that Moscow is deeply concerned over the war 
in Yemen which is continuing and called for a ceasefire between 
the two warring parties. 

